                        <text>
                            <p>  	  Indicates this is the sending NCRS compliant GP system .  </p>
                            <p>The Coded with Code System datatype flavour is used to carry this information as follows:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>The <i>code</i> attribute will contain the value "SND" from the list of codes in the <u>SystemRoleType</u> vocabulary <br/>
